==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pasteboard
<hw>Paste"board`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
stiff thick kind of paper board, formed of several single sheets pasted
one upon another, or of paper macerated and pressed into molds,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Cookery)</fld> <def>A board on which pastry dough
is rolled; a molding board.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>pasted</ent>⟦br⟧
